titles.title: Electing certain Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 2/26/2013--Passed House without amendment. Elects specified Members to the following House Committees: (1) Agriculture, (2) Appropriations, (3) the Budget, and (4) Ways and Means.
